&gt; This might not not be the right place to pose this question, but I just
&gt; got curios. What exactly could happen if you put back a Connection to
&gt; your pool without for instance closing a statement created with this
&gt; Connection ?
&gt; In the beginning of my programming &#39;career&#39; I wrote lots of code never
&gt; worrying about those things, and I never noticed anything bad
&gt; happening....
&gt; I&#39;m still quite a bit of a newbie but now I close my stuff, yet I don&#39;t
